{"tid":1573173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全民救手足","createTime":"2019-09-16T01:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T02:16:23.000Z","uid":294825,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3e368446363eb5315cb57eebec95ffb04e3cd87a","tid":1573173,"uid":294825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:55:00.000Z","msg":"現場嘅人可以用呢個方法集合自己人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ayo7KGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAyo7KGf.jpg&h=25d34270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一個人大叫1！第二個人大叫2！之後3！4！5！<br />\n夠五個可以上<br />\n當人數到五個或以上嘅時候就一齊向前救人<br />\n因為大多數人唔夠膽上前都係因為怕自己孤立無援，咁樣唔單止可以有比較清晰指示幾時進攻，<br />\n仲可以有足夠人手去打狗救人"},{"pid":"2f14de1c17f16b27ab54e02a5fc59fb5f8710ffb","tid":1573173,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"開啟新戰線：「天滅中共 平反六四」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正式輸出革命<br />\n<br />\n係大陸人比較多嘅地方，<br />\neg. ifc國歌集會，上水羅湖落馬洲邊境，大學內地生（NDS) 聚腳場合<br />\n<br />\n1）不斷傳播解放軍89六四當年鎮壓市民真相<br />\n<br />\n2）瘋狂播《血染的風采》，播到中共連每日150單程證都唔夠膽放落嚟為止，彭麗媛版本更理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）要將「天滅中共，平反六四」加入為一主要口號，用國語讀更佳<br />\n（香港人終於connect 法輪功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=utvG-uwDsD8&amp;list=RDutvG-uwDsD8&amp;start_radio=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DutvG-uwDsD8%26list%3DRDutvG-uwDsD8%26start_r